rows.label: qst201407_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh, Hikari and Zakuro! Could you be
in the midst of your big Girl-off?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0002
rows.name: Oh! Saika!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0003
rows.name:
We need you to judge us on our
Girl Power-driven chatting skills.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0004
rows.name:
Sounds fun.
I'm game.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0005
rows.name: So what do we talk about?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0006
rows.name:
So far we've done favorite foods and...
romance-talk...

rows.label: qst201407_msg0007
rows.name: Oh yeah? Romance-talk, huh?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0008
rows.name:
So... Do you two have a certain special
someone in your sights?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0009
rows.name:
Ah, well that's certainly an interesting
topic...but there's no one right now.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0010
rows.name: Erm...same here.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0011
rows.name:
Oh, Hikari... You're a closed book,
aren't you?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0012
rows.name:
I think there is someone.
A certain...

rows.label: qst201407_msg0013
rows.name: NO! There's no one. I swear!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0014
rows.name:
What about you, Saika?
Who do you like?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0015
rows.name: Yeah! 'Fess up!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0016
rows.name:
What about Zeke?
Do you think that could go somewhere?

rows.label: qst201407_msg0017
rows.name:
N-no! I...I don't think of the Prince like
that!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0018
rows.name:
He's so pig-headed and insensitive.
Nothing gets through to him.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0019
rows.name:
I think you must have been paying a
fair bit of attention to him, to make an
observation like that.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0020
rows.name: What do you really think? Tell me!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0021
rows.name: No, no, no, no!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0022
rows.name: I won't tell you!

rows.label: qst201407_msg0023
rows.name: There she goes.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0024
rows.name: Saika's surprisingly shy, huh.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0025
rows.name:
Well, we've lost another judge.
I guess it's another draw.

rows.label: qst201407_msg0026
rows.name: Oh, well. Can't be helped!
